    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Abstract wordless images made on paper using a typewriter as a mark-making device. Coined by Edwin Morgan to describe the works of Dom Sylvester Houédard.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
